(Jesus!). Meanwhile he can‚Äôt shout at her and has to be this consoling
fuck of a person (I told him to not shout too). This is what I
gathered from the phone call. Maybe he is to blame for being incapable
to ‚Äúhelp her‚Äù but nevertheless, there is so much drama now atleast.</p>

<p>P.S: He swiftly immediately said that, this shall in no way be
considered as a point against marriage. Haha!</p>

<p><strong>Definition</strong>: checks out</p>

<p><strong>Checklist</strong>:  yes; true;</p>

<p>Although, if this is the case throughout the lifetime, I am
unsure. Kids happen, kids education needs to happen, kids need to go
to college and get a respectable job and get married to a good girl
(;)) etc‚Ä¶ It might follow you intermittently say every 5 years I
guess. Moving on.</p>

<h2 id="disturbance-to-donations">Disturbance to donations</h2>

<p><strong>Claims</strong>: Raising kids needs a lot of money</p>

<p><strong>Example</strong>: In the case of my x-colleague, he is expected to spend
5k‚Ç¨ per year on raising the kid (along with say around 1-2 hrs at
home). 5k‚Ç¨ per year is 100k‚Ç¨ in 20 years. His wife is also working
full time, so that becomes, 50k‚Ç¨ pp. In addition lets say he needs to
devote 1 full hour every day for 20 years = 20x365x15‚Ç¨ = 109k‚Ç¨pp</p>

<p>My parents spent say 50k rs a year on me (11k‚Ç¨)+ bachelors education
(8k‚Ç¨) + Masters education (50k‚Ç¨). With a total of 69k‚Ç¨. And in case I
get married, they will pay atleast another 10k‚Ç¨. They have two kids so
that is roughly 150k‚Ç¨ to raise two kids. So 75k‚Ç¨ pp.</p>

<p>Contrast this to what I save now and expect to save in the coming
years:</p>

<p>If I donate 10% and stay in a similar job as I am currently with a
growth of 5%, I could potentially donate 174k‚Ç¨ over a 20 year period.</p>

<p><strong>Definition</strong>: To conclude, If I raise a kid it costs 75k to 150k‚Ç¨ pp
including time spent. This is a lot of money considering, a 10%
donation repeated over 20 years is 174k‚Ç¨. If I take the money on kids
and donate it as well, I could potentially double my contribution or
save another 38 people over the next 20 years.</p>

<p><strong>Checklist</strong>: yes; true;</p>

<hr />

<p><strong>Claims</strong>: Wife will consume lots of money</p>

