<p><strong>Definition</strong>: checks out. It doesn‚Äôt seem to be as bad as having kids.</p>

<p><strong>Checklist</strong>: yes; true;</p>

<hr />

<p><del><strong>Claims</strong>: When you have wife and kids your donations reduces</del></p>

